{"tid":2436824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"識個朋友中產出身，佢說服咗自己老豆老母去打科興。","createTime":"2021-03-07T12:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:40:18.000Z","uid":32051,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af5d5687488200a0dc5812e7e5316ad627949e6c","tid":2436824,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"佢份人由細到大都唔多嘢講，又估唔到佢咁叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n氹得掂家中兩老去接受西洋醫術，真係去打疫苗喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為佢全家由細到大都好似話只會睇中醫；從來唔食西藥。<br />\n<br />\n真係覺得好正面，想share俾大家知。<br />\n說服多d人接種科興，達至群體免疫。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享，愛的訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693b37b5ad7367dd7889873ef1cc29daa54c1e43","tid":2436824,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"淨袋4球, 爽yy"},{"pid":"9f37d66406456a22978dd2a55d94a32751e3ae8c","tid":2436824,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩老唔想個仔咁辛苦，幫個仔博下四百萬<br />\n<br />\n父愛母愛真偉大"},{"pid":"51e93cf96ce51ae1ff77ff162b371ba4954adaef","tid":2436824,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"留低既都係一份心意"},{"pid":"738136307bb2573200065b2515dbda4a262b7cd8","tid":2436824,"uid":247184,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"693b37b5ad7367dd7889873ef1cc29daa54c1e43","tid":2436824,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"淨袋4球, 爽yy"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"跟本無得賠，只係想要遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e5a78f361c7f0774447662ec5c2c36ccaad691","tid":2436824,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"693b37b5ad7367dd7889873